\int_A Xd\mathbb Q=\int_A E^\mathbb Q[X\mid \mathcal G]d\mathbb Q,\quad\forall A\in\mathcal G.
\int_A Xd\mathbb Q=\int_A \frac{E^\mathbb P[Xf\mid \mathcal G]}{E^\mathbb P[f\mid \mathcal G]}d\mathbb Q,\quad\forall A\in\mathcal G.
\tilde{\mathbb P}=\left.\mathbb P\right|_\mathcal G
\mathbb E^\mathbb P[f\mid \mathcal G]=\dfrac{d\tilde{\mathbb P}}{d\tilde{\mathbb Q}}.
